                <h1>RLHS takes measures to stop bed bugs</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/172a09a6-cfbc-42de-92f1-4f765de2e257.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="In&#x20;light&#x20;of&#x20;rising&#x20;complaints&#x20;across&#x20;the&#x20;country&#x20;of&#x20;bed&#x20;bug&#x20;infestations,&#x20;RLHS&#x20;is&#x20;taking&#x20;measures&#x20;to&#x20;prevent&#x20;the&#x20;insects&#x20;from&#x20;permeating&#x20;the&#x20;University." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            In light of rising complaints across the country of bed bug infestations, RLHS is taking measures to prevent the insects from permeating the University.

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/tracy-huang-the-chronicle">Tracy Huang/ The Chronicle</a> |
                                                                                                                                The Chronicle
                                                                            </figcaption>
                                </aside>
                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/lauren-carroll">Lauren Carroll</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">October 19, 2010 | 4:00am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
