                        <p>For students from those regions, the concern at home is much more prevalent than at Duke. In New York City, the bed bug epidemic has become a main topic of local media and daily conversation, said Lucas Spangher, a freshman from Long Island. </p>
<p>“I know a lot of people who have [changed] because of it,” he said, “They’ve gone out and bought bed bug control.” </p>

